      • GanttChartGUI

        public GanttChartGUI(boolean use_internal_copy)
        Constructs a Gantt Chart with custom node policy. If use_internal_copy is true, all jobs are duplicated. If false, the jobs are stored references, and the chart will respond to external changes.
        Parameters:
        use_internal_copy - whether the nodes will duplicate the jobs internally, or store only references.
